flowchart LR
    AXME[AXME Platform]

    AXME --> CLOUD[Cloud SaaS\ncustomer uses shared infra]
    AXME --> PRIV[Private Cloud\ncustomer VPC / region]
    AXME --> ON[On-Premises\ncustomer data center]

    CLOUD --> SHARE[shared control plane]
    PRIV --> DED[dedicated control plane]
    ON --> LOCAL[fully isolated\nno egress required]

    SHARE & DED & LOCAL --> UNIFIED[unified API surface\nsame SDK + spec]
